8 service of minimum percentage of sentence; conforming
language; authorizing lower minimum imprisonment
9 requirement; authorizing district attorney to file
certain notice; requiring district attorney to
10 consider certain factors; repealing 21 O.S. 2021,
Section 13.1, as amended by Section 5, Chapter 59,
11 O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 13.1), which
relates to required service of minimum percentage of
12 sentence; repealing 21 O.S. 2021, Section 13.1, as
last amended by Section 2, Chapter 18, O.S.L. 2025
13 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 13.1), which relates to
required service of minimum percentage of sentence;
14 repealing 21 O.S. 2021, Section 13.1, as last amended
by Section 1, Chapter 352, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp.
15 2025, Section 13.1), which relates to required
service of minimum percentage of sentence; and
16 providing an effective date.
