19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
20 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 13.1, as
21 last amended by Section 1, Chapter 162, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp.
22 2025, Section 13.1), is amended to read as follows:
23 Section 13.1. A. Persons convicted of:
