3 SECTION 2. REPEALER 21 O.S. 2021, Section 13.1, as
4 amended by Section 5, Chapter 59, O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
5 Section 13.1), is hereby repealed.
6 SECTION 3. REPEALER 21 O.S. 2021, Section 13.1, as last
7 amended by Section 2, Chapter 18, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
8 Section 13.1), is hereby repealed.
9 SECTION 4. REPEALER 21 O.S. 2021, Section 13.1, as last
10 amended by Section 1, Chapter 352, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
11 Section 13.1), is hereby repealed.
12 SECTION 5. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
